# Project Context
This is Project Chimera, an autonomous influencer infrastructure system.

# Prime Directive
NEVER generate code without checking specs/ first.

# Java Directives
- Strictly adhere to Java 21+ idioms.
- Use Java `record` for immutable DTOs passed between Planner/Worker/Judge.
- Use JUnit 5 for all generated tests.
- Use virtual-thread based concurrency for worker execution where appropriate.

# Traceability and Governance
- Explain your plan before writing code.
- Keep all external interactions behind MCP boundaries.
- Apply HITL policy and confidence thresholds before action finalization.
